   January 30, 2002         DOL > E-mail to a Friend

   E-mail to a Friend


   We believe in protecting your privacy. When you send an e-mail message
   from our site, no identifying information will be used. Your friend
   will receive a message from "email2friend@dol.gov". There is no way to
   reply to this e-mail address. For further information, read our
   privacy statement.

   Link to send:

   Send this link to: Send an optional message below.
   The URL for the page will be added to your message automatically.
   ___________________________________
   Type the e-mail address of the recipient(s). To send this link to
   multiple recipients, separate the addresses with semicolons (without
   spaces).

